{"tid":1665661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【偷步買樓】聶德權與妻愛炒樓 五買四沽賺逾700萬","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T16:23:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5621bed234643a2bbafc9045018e8cd9d5e8d0b2","tid":1665661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191020/60175103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191020%2F60175103&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=091542a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191020%2F60175103&h=cc4246b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191020/60175103</a><br />\n<br />\n【偷步買樓】聶德權與妻愛炒樓 五買四沽賺逾700萬<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n【新增資料表及影片】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高官醜聞！聶德權涉偷步買樓 施政報告公佈前家人購2深水埗樓花<br />\n<br />\n身兼行政會議官守成員的政制及內地事務局局長聶德權，在《施政報告》公佈前兩周，知會行政會議秘書處更新利益申報紀錄，新加入一項物業資料，涉及兩個位於深水埗區的住宅樓花，昨日被揭發後報稱涉事單位業權百分百由家人擁有，今早聶德權在個人facebook專頁，再就事件解釋，並表示抱歉，重申有關交易是屬家人的決定，亦強調自己是完全沒有參與和業權。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，聶德權與妻子張翠蘭過去買樓出手頻繁，2000年後他們聯名先後買入5個物業，當中沽出4個合共賺超過700萬元。目前以他們名義持有的本港物業有1伙，為2008年以800萬元買入沙田曉翠山莊實用1,328方呎單位，目前市值約1,787萬元，11年升值逾1.2倍。<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，聶德權與妻子在90年代買樓，1992年以313萬元買入西灣河鯉景灣1個單位後，持貨至1995年以350萬元沽出，賬面賺約37萬元。1995年他們聯名以543萬元買入太古城海景花園碧藤閣1個中層3房單位，1997年樓市高峰期再聯名以448萬元再買多1個太古城興安閣的單位。其後亞洲金融風暴，碧藤閣的單位在1999年以505萬元沽出，蝕38萬元。另一個位於興安閣的單位持有至2007年沽出，持貨10年，賬面仍蝕18萬元。<br />\n<br />\n摸頂買太古城蝕讓後，未有打消買樓念頭。2000年至2010年期間先後5次入市，繼續與妻子聯名買樓，包括買入灣仔星域軒1伙，持貨5年賺264萬元；新蒲崗譽港灣1伙，持貨2年賺約328萬元；沙田聚龍居1伙，持貨1年賺10萬元；大角嘴君匯港1伙，持貨3年賺143.2萬元。沽出4個單位合共賺逾700萬元。<br />\n<br />\n尚未沽出單位為2008年以800萬元買入的沙田曉翠山莊低層單位，實用1,328方呎，持有至今，根據滙豐銀行網上物業估價對這個單位的估值為1,787萬元。<br />\n<br />\n根據行會秘書處網頁資料，聶德權的利益申報資料，在本港持有4個物業，分佈於沙田及深水埗，1個與配偶各擁50%業權，料為上述沙田曉翠山莊，另外3個深水埗物業由家人擁100%業權，當中2個為未建成單位。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191020/large/1571560034_85bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191020%2Flarge%2F1571560034_85bb.jpg&h=b570dde1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政制及內地事務局長聶德權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191020/large/1571569793_b421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191020%2Flarge%2F1571569793_b421.jpg&h=80665b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191020/large/1571569793_a8f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191020%2Flarge%2F1571569793_a8f6.jpg&h=26c3c4c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【短片】【雙紅會●不斷更新】開波！紅軍缺沙拿 兩隊門神齊回歸<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【短片】【抗暴之戰】水炮車瘋狂發射清真寺變藍 警高層派下屬清潔「贖罪」<br />\n<br />\n高官醜聞！聶德權涉偷步買樓 施政報告公佈前家人購2深水埗樓花"},{"pid":"5cc97766670c5cec28cb4a1ed456ba1644b4e02c","tid":1665661,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"好叻仔喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ef4488164ad78b338660f7d6dbddb7ffa3eb33","tid":1665661,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第十期牆紙］訴求在沉默中進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=d5b2bcd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n歡迎投稿 : <a href=\"https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Flennonnewshk%2F6g5yp3tllkxx&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=59059ed2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx</a>"},{"pid":"b150fb8b0fa37fa53b982eab912fea5f4d51ab92","tid":1665661,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"點解上次對佢咁仁慈？"},{"pid":"f5fbf0e5d6bc3c3e86d725bf5286ef518155bf30","tid":1665661,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"ICAC一定又睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />689又係咁"},{"pid":"87a248a7814e49f93a579bbb1a90500b73c508d0","tid":1665661,"uid":223531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}